health care facilities providers

   We've created this special page for health care facilities providers.
   It contains information, from all parts of HUD's web site, that will
   interest you - it gives you one-stop shopping!

   We hope you will bookmark this page and return to it frequently. And if
   you have suggestions for additional information that we should add to
   this page, please let us know.

